SUMMARY:*** 10 AM Hilly Walk in NW Portland Forest Heights Trails
DESCRIPTION:Portland City Trail Walking Group\nMeet outside Jim & Patty's Coffee\, 2021 NW Miller Rd\, Portland 97229. We'll walk the trails within the Forest Heights neighborhood. About 4 hilly miles with 700 feet of elevation.
