SUMMARY:**10 AM** Walk to Coffee in SW Portland **10 AM**
DESCRIPTION:Portland City Trail Walking Group\nHilly 5 miles roundtrip down about 450' from the Hillsdale Library to Elephant's Deli on SW Corbett Ave.\nAbout 25 minutes for coffee break\, then return to start\, passing thru the Hillsdale Farmer's Market (if it’s open). NOTE: Sections of the hike are steep & hilly\, and are not recommended for people who are new to hiking.
